{"id":456,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":456,"title":"Job 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Satan obtains permission from the Lord to afflict Job physically—Job is smitten with boils—Eliphaz, Bildad, and Zophar come to comfort him."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.1","order":"02.19.002.33019"},["b","1"],"Again there was a day when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"sons"],"of God came to present themselves before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Satan"],"came also among them to present himself before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.2","order":"02.19.002.33020"},["b","2"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Satan, From whence comest thou? And Satan answered the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and said, From going to and fro in the earth, and from walking up and down in it."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.3","order":"02.19.002.33021"},["b","3"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Satan, Hast thou considered my servant Job, that",["i","there is"],"none like him in the earth, a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"perfect"],"and an upright man, one that feareth God, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"escheweth"],"evil? and still he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"holdeth"],"fast his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"integrity"],", although thou movedst me against him, to destroy him without cause."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.4","order":"02.19.002.33022"},["b","4"],"And Satan answered the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and said, Skin for skin, yea, all that a man hath will he give for his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"life"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.5","order":"02.19.002.33023"},["b","5"],"But put forth thine hand now, and touch his bone and his flesh, and he will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"curse"],"thee to thy face."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.6","order":"02.19.002.33024"},["b","6"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Satan, Behold, he",["i","is"],"in thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hand"],"; but save his life."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.7","order":"02.19.002.33025"},["b","7"],"¶So went Satan forth from the presence of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and smote Job with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"sore"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"boils"],"from the sole of his foot unto his crown."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.8","order":"02.19.002.33026"},["b","8"],"And he took him a potsherd to scrape himself withal; and he sat down among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"ashes"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.9","order":"02.19.002.33027"},["b","9"],"¶Then said his wife unto him, Dost thou still",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"retain"],"thine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"integrity"],"?",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"curse"],"God, and die."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.10","order":"02.19.002.33028"},["b","10"],"But he said unto her, Thou speakest as one of the foolish women speaketh. What? shall we receive",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"good"],"at the hand of God, and shall we not receive",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"evil"],"? In all this did not Job",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sin"],"with his lips."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.11","order":"02.19.002.33029"},["b","11"],"¶Now when Job’s three",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"friends"],"heard of all this evil that was come upon him, they came every one from his own place; Eliphaz the Temanite, and Bildad the Shuhite, and Zophar the Naamathite: for they had made an appointment together to come to mourn with him and to comfort him."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.12","order":"02.19.002.33030"},["b","12"],"And when they lifted up their eyes afar off, and knew him not, they lifted up their voice, and wept; and they rent every one his mantle, and sprinkled dust upon their heads toward heaven."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.13","order":"02.19.002.33031"},["b","13"],"So they sat down with him upon the ground",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"seven"],"days and seven nights, and none spake a word unto him: for they saw that",["i","his"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"grief"],"was very great."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.1a","order":"02.19.002.33032"},["b","1a"],["span.small","JST"],"Job 2:1 …",["i","children"],"…"],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.1b","order":"02.19.002.33034"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.3a","order":"02.19.002.33036"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"blameless.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perfection"},"TG Perfection"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.3b","order":"02.19.002.33038"},["b","3b"],["span.small","HEB"],"turns from."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.3c","order":"02.19.002.33040"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perseverance"},"TG Perseverance"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.3d","order":"02.19.002.33042"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/integrity"},"TG Integrity"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.4a","order":"02.19.002.33044"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mortality"},"TG Mortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.5a","order":"02.19.002.33046"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.6a","order":"02.19.002.33048"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/probation"},"TG Probation"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.7a","order":"02.19.002.33050"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.7b","order":"02.19.002.33052"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/38.21"},"Isa. 38:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.8a","order":"02.19.002.33054"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/42.6"},"Job 42:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.21"},"Matt. 11:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.25"},"Mosiah 11:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.9a","order":"02.19.002.33056"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perseverance"},"TG Perseverance"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.9b","order":"02.19.002.33058"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/steadfastness"},"TG Steadfastness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.9c","order":"02.19.002.33060"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blaspheme"},"TG Blaspheme"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.10a","order":"02.19.002.33062"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.45"},"Matt. 5:45"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.11"},"2 Ne. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.39"},"D&C 29:39"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.7.5-9"},"122:7 (5–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/patience"},"TG Patience"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.10b","order":"02.19.002.33064"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/evil"},"TG Evil"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.10c","order":"02.19.002.33066"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/1.22"},"Job 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.11a","order":"02.19.002.33068"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.1.1-8"},"Job 4:1 (1–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.13a","order":"02.19.002.33070"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/50.10"},"Gen. 50:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.13b","order":"02.19.002.33072"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.12"},"Hel. 5:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.8"},"D&C 24:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.7.1-9"},"122:7 (1–9)"],"."]]}
